<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan></del> Grafen vnd / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l19"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü kaſtel / . </ab>
</div>
