<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l21"><expan>Andr<ex>es</ex></expan> <expan>Lampr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd begert daʒ wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l22">
<add><ab facs="#facs_316_r2l1">Jm </ab></add> geleitte cʒü vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wenn er cʒü vns kum <expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l23">vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag <expan>Aſſumpcio<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> nu ſchirſt / Das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l24">wöllen wir durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün / Alſo wenn er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l25"><expan>hiecʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frawen tag cʒü vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l26"><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil / So ſüllen er vnd die ſeinen die mit Jm cʒü vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l27">kumen / dreÿ tag ein ſleht geleitte <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> beÿ vns in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l28">Stat für allermenıklıch / vnd cʒü vns vnd von vns für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_316_r3l29">vns vnd die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> / . vnd wo vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
